main event: Two witnesses observed a triangular or V-shaped object in the sky over Tupper Lake, New York on September 24, 1963.
interesting points: The object was surrounded by streaks of light or trails., The image of the UFO is grainy and in black and white., The investigation was conducted by Major Hector Quintanilla, Jr., The report is part of Project Blue Book., It was noted that there is 1 photo related to this sighting.
sighted object: triangular or V-shaped object in the sky
